---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home" description="Yilong Scrubs - 20 Years of Precision. 100% Focused on Your Comfort. Discover professional-grade medical scrubs engineered for performance, durability, and a perfect fit.">
  <section class="relative h-[650px] flex items-center bg-primary text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 z-10">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">20 Years of Precision.<br/><span class="text-secondary underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8">100% Focused</span> on Your Comfort.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mb-10 text-slate-100 leading-relaxed">
        Discover professional-grade medical scrubs engineered for performance, durability, and a perfect fit. Crafted with OEKO-TEX® certified fabrics and a legacy of manufacturing excellence.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/products" class="bg-secondary px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-emerald-600 transition shadow-lg">Explore Collections</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition">Get a Custom Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary/80 to-transparent opacity-95"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Yilong Difference</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-16 text-lg">Building trust through quality and reliability for over two decades.</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
        <div class="p-10 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">20-Year Heritage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Two decades of specialized manufacturing experience in the global medical apparel market.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-10 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-emerald-50 text-secondary flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">100% Scrubs Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We don't just make uniforms; we specialize exclusively in scrubs, ensuring unmatched expertise in every stitch.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-10 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Flexible Low MOQ</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Starting your brand? Our low minimum order quantities (10-50 sets) make professional customization accessible for everyone.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Certified Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">All fabrics are OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified, ensuring they are safe for your skin and the environment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Fabric Systems Highlights</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">The foundation of every Yilong scrub set is our commitment to textile excellence.</p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-primary font-bold text-xl">205GSM</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Premium Series</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Maximum durability for demanding shifts. High-intensity performance.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-secondary font-bold text-xl">180GSM</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Standard Series</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500">The ultimate balance of comfort and performance. Perfect for daily shifts.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-xl">130GSM</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Lightweight Series</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Breathable, agile, and perfect for active professionals in warm climates.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary h-[500px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative">
          <!-- Image Placeholder -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 text-8xl font-black uppercase rotate-12">YILONG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
